Class LogUnitClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.corfudb.runtime.clients.LogUnitClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IClient

    public class LogUnitClient
extends Object
implements IClient
    A client to a LogUnit. This class provides access to operations on a remote log unit. Created by mwei on 12/10/15.
